quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  38,62,"BewЙ“e townitiiЙ“e Й“en wi'a: Ko haЙ—i men yi'ugol ka Yiite gaa, worЙ“e Й“e men limtaynoo ka aduna, jeyaaЙ“e e bomЙ“e, hannduЙ“e e lepte?"
  38,63,"Hara men falju e kon men jagitornoo Й“e kon jalnori, tawa Й“e handaa e lepte, kaa hara Й“e naatu Yiite, gite amen yawti Й“e?"
  38,64,"Pellet, ko Men jantanii on kon, e ko yedduЙ“e Й“en wenjorndirta hakkunde maЙ“Й“e Г‘alnde Darngal, ko goonga mo sikke alaa e mu'un."
  38,65,"An Muhammadu, maakan yimЙ“e maa yedduЙ“e Й“en: Anndee ko mi jertinoowo on, e lepte Allah Й—en, fii wata Й—e yanir e mon, sabu yeddugol mon fenna NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. Anndo kadi, alaa reweteeЙ—o hannduЙ—o e dewal, si wanaa Allah SeniiЙ—o On. Ko Kanko woni Bajjo ka mawngu e sifaaji e ka inЙ—e Mun, FooluЙ—o kala huunde. Mo huunde kala yankinii ЖЉum."
  38,66,"Ko Kanko woni JeyЙ—o kammuuli Й—in, e leydi ndin, e kon ko woni hakkunde majji. FooluЙ—o e laamu Mun, Mo gooto foolataa. Haforoowo junuubi jeyaaЙ“e Makko tuubuЙ“e Й“en."
  38,67,"An NulaaЙ—o, maakan Й“ee fennooЙ“e : ndee Alqur'aanaare, ko kumpital mawngal fiyaaku."
  38,68,"Kono hiЙ—on Й—uurnii e on kabaaru mawnuЙ—o fiyaaku. On alaa yeЖґЖґitaade e makko."
  38,69,"Mi heЙ“ataano ganndal, e ko feЖґЖґaynoo hakkunde Malaa'ika'en, fii tagugol Aadama, si wanaano Allah wahayini Й—um e am, O anndimmi."
  38,70,"Allah wahayiniraali e am, si wanaa tawde ko mi jertinoowo on, e lepte Makko Й—en, Й“anninano on."
  38,71,"Janto nde Joomi maa daalannoo Malaa'ika'en: Min ko Mi tagiroowo Й“anndinke, woni Aadama (yo o his) immorde e loopal."
  38,72,"Si Mi fotindirii tagu makko ngun, Mi moЖґЖґintinii mbaadi makko ndin, mi wuttii ruuhu Am on e makko, ko yo on sujjan mo."
  38,73,"Malaa'ika'en Й—oftii yamaruyee Joomi maЙ“Й“e on, Й“e sujji Й“e denndaangal, sujuudu teddungal. Alaa mo sujjanaano Aadama e maЙ“Й“e."
  38,74,"Si wanaa Ibuliisa, o mawnitinii sujjugol ngol, o woni jeyaaЙ—o e yedduЙ“e Joomi mun."
  38,75,"Allah daali: Ko an yo Ibuliisa, ko honЙ—um haЙ—u maa sujjangol Aadama, mo tagirmi juuЙ—e Am? Ko mawnintinaare haЙ—u maa kaa hari nun ko a jeyanooЙ—o e townitaniiЙ“e Joomi mun Й“en?"
  38,76,"Ibuliisa wi'i: Ko min Й“uri Aadama moЖґЖґude. Tawde A tagirii lam immorde e yiite, A tagirii mo kanko e loopal. Sikkugol mo wonnde yiite Й“uri loope teddude."
  38,77,"Alla daalani ibuliisa: Yaltu ka Aljanna ton, sabu ko a huЙ—aaЙ—o KiitaaЙ—a."
  38,78,"Pellet, raЙ—eede ka Aljanna fawike ma, haa Г‘alaande nЙ“jodi kuuЙ—e, nden woni Г‘alnde Darngal."
  38,79,"Ibuliisa wi'i: Nennitanam maayugol, haa Г±alnde immintaa jeyaaЙ“e Maa Й“en."
  38,80,"Allah daali: A jeyaama e nennitanaaЙ“e Й“en."
  38,81,"A nennitanaama, haa e happu anndaaЙ—o, halkeede ma."
  38,82,"Ibuliisa wi'i: Mi woondirii kattal e mawngu Maa ngun ! Ma mi majjin Й“iЙ—Й“e Aadama Й“en fow."
  38,83,"Si wanaa Й“en Й“e daЙ—ndu-ЖЉaa bone am, heertinir-ЖЉaa Й“e e rewugol Am tun."